==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Infelicitous
<hw>In`fe*lic"i*tous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not
felicitous; unhappy; unfortunate; not fortunate or appropriate in
application; not well said, expressed, or done; <as>as, an
<ex>infelicitous</ex> condition; an <ex>infelicitous</ex> remark; an
<ex>infelicitous</ex> description; <ex>infelicitous</ex>
words.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Infelicity</ent>⟦br⟧
